{"tid":430138,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點先算「乖」？","createTime":"2017-10-09T14:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T15:05:23.000Z","uid":29218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f60c83e1394455054088e5028c0c6efc547994e","tid":430138,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:04:44.000Z","msg":"很多人以為「乖」即係聽話 順從 服從 <br />\n其實大錯特錯 <br />\n<br />\n《說文》：乖，戾也 <br />\n即 違背、「唔聽話」之意 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」可表示分離。南朝梁任昉〈與沈約書〉：「將乖之際，不忍告別。」 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」也表示隔絕、斷絕。宋歐陽修〈清平樂〉：「別來音信全乖，舊期前事堪猜。」 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」還表示差異、不同。晉葛洪《抱樸子‧辭義》：「五味舛而並甘，眾色乖而皆麗。」 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」也指反常、謬誤。《禮記‧樂記》：「亂世之音怨以怒，其政乖。」 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」還指不順利、不如意。唐韓愈〈贈崔立之評事〉：「時命雖乖心轉壯，技能虛富家逾窘。」 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」亦表示機靈、聰明。唐李廓〈上令狐舍人〉：「宿客嫌吟苦，乖童恨睡遲。」 <br />\n<br />\n「乖」也可指不淘氣、馴服。《西游記》第42回：「好乖兒女，也罷也罷，向前開路，我和你去來。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=乖\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%E4%B9%96&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5bDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=389d64e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=乖</a><br />\n<br />\n上述例子中<br />\n只有表示機智聰明時的「乖」才有正面意思<br />\n例如乖巧<br />\n但這種「乖」，其實是白話文別字的「佳」<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/9kJRkP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9kJRkP&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5bDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=f73867e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/9kJRkP</a><br />\n河洛話一千零一頁(卷二K~P): 一分鐘悅讀河洛話<br />\n<br />\n「乖」真正意思同近代人理解的順從大相逕庭<br />\n但綜合各種意思<br />\n乖又可有另一正面理解<br />\n「乖」的人 是獨立 卓然不群 聰明的 是包受挫折而不被馴服<br />\n如是者 做個「乖」人亦無不可<br />\n若果事事盲從 那就真的不「乖」了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原文：<a href=\"http://hkgalden.com/view/446508/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkgalden.com%2Fview%2F446508%2F&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5bDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=fef23f42\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkgalden.com/view/446508/</a></span>"},{"pid":"453ca752fe4fa36bc1028099cd558901e69c97e3","tid":430138,"uid":34444,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"689咁咪乖 成隻狗咁"},{"pid":"d7a494bf0ba14382b70444c1b96b63de2e65f11e","tid":430138,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"現代可以用戇鳩入替"},{"pid":"9e9109a6e581f0fc870cce22ae96eb6aa18a7468","tid":430138,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ff8daf86850189a33697e322dd26ee5e35ec1c","tid":430138,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高質絲打"},{"pid":"15dc3b0bb1f3d453dc55690442c1aadd28b9586a","tid":430138,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0da76102210a6c3729854d3d4074aaea0654ecf3","tid":430138,"uid":37585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"呢個年代毒撚咪乖lor，根本乖係呢個社會只會俾人利用"},{"pid":"113cd4e4baa5e0846cb55e453b4ddbaa4b07c025","tid":430138,"uid":48624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/22BWWOtcoVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F22BWWOtcoVc&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5bDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=bf3b7df0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/22BWWOtcoVc</a>"}]}